I wish i had never known you! (April 9, 2015)

I wish I had never known you. I was happy before even when you were not there yet. Unlike now, you make me suffer, I know that you didn't mean to have known me. Me too, I wasn't planning on liking you.

But I have learned something. You should find a person who calls you gorgeous instead of hot, who calls you back when you hang up on, who will lie under the stars and listen to your heartbeat, or will stay awake just to watch you sleep... wait for the right person who kisses your forehead, who wants to show you off to the world when you are in sweats, who holds your hand in front of his friends, who thinks you' re just as attractive without anything on. One who is constantly reminding you of how much he cares and how lucky he is to have YOU... The one who turns to his friends and says, thats him...

We should always have in mind that the ones we like the most are usually the ones whom hurt you the most.

And to whoever you are, I just wished to be liked not because I am stable, or good, or well bred, or agile, or intelligent, but because of who I am and what I can be with you.

Hope it's you whom I can hold hands with while watching the sunset......

